WEBVTT

00:01:10.840 --> 00:01:11.240
Ma Guangfu.

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:12.160
Don't come closer. If you take another step,

00:01:12.160 --> 00:01:13.039
I'll jump!

00:01:13.280 --> 00:01:14.240
I'll jump!

00:01:14.240 --> 00:01:14.800
Ma Guangfu,

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:15.640
come down first.

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:16.200
Let's have a good talk.

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:17.440
There's nothing to talk about.

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:18.080
Yan,

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:20.660
if you hadn't thrown me in jail back then,

00:01:20.760 --> 00:01:22.560
my wife wouldn't have been left alone,

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:25.000
and we would've had money for her treatment!

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:27.120
You are the ones who killed my wife!

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:28.120
You were arrested back then

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:29.320
because you hit and ran,

00:01:29.320 --> 00:01:30.280
causing a fatality.

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:32.320
If you commit a crime, you have to pay the price.

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.450
You clearly had a chance to start over.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:36.979
Why did you bomb innocent people?

00:01:38.160 --> 00:01:40.120
They deserved to die!

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:42.320
They got in your car.

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:45.560
You are the one who deserves to die,

00:01:45.600 --> 00:01:47.240
not them.

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:49.160
All of you

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:50.840
act high and mighty,

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.240
full of morality and justice.

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:54.759
You completely forgot

00:01:54.759 --> 00:01:56.960
how ordinary people live.

00:01:57.240 --> 00:01:59.360
I just wanted to haul goods to support my family.

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:00.640
Was I wrong?

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:02.240
I'm telling you,

00:02:02.760 --> 00:02:05.880
you are the ones who destroyed my family!

00:02:05.920 --> 00:02:07.720
You are the ones who should die.

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:10.680
I won't let you off even if I become a ghost.

00:02:34.480 --> 00:02:34.960
Dad.

00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:36.200
Mom.

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.000
Prioritize the investigation.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:49.480
Okay.

00:02:50.320 --> 00:02:50.960
Yan.

00:02:53.720 --> 00:02:54.360
Mr. Yan.

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:55.400
Get in the car.

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:13.520
Qiao Sisi.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:14.920
Five years ago,

00:03:14.920 --> 00:03:17.050
she worked as a hostess at Huguang KTV.

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.600
After Huguang closed down,

00:03:18.600 --> 00:03:20.000
she has been unemployed.

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.880
Starting eight months ago,

00:03:21.880 --> 00:03:23.680
every month, her bank account

00:03:24.079 --> 00:03:25.680
would receive a sum of money.

00:03:26.079 --> 00:03:27.320
Where did the money come from?

00:03:27.320 --> 00:03:29.240
It was wired from an overseas account.

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:31.280
The last payment date was

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.400
five days before the crime.

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:33.000
Overseas?

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:34.560
Given Qiao Sisi's social circle...

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:35.800
How could there be overseas contact?

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:36.480
Did you check?

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:38.520
We've sent a request to other units for assistance.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.520
But since it involves overseas,

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:40.480
it's quite complicated.

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:42.740
So we might not get results anytime soon.

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:45.320
What about Kong Jiao?

00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:46.280
What's the background check result?

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:47.640
Just like Qiao Sisi,

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:48.360
five years ago,

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.520
they were both hostesses at Huguang KTV.

00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:51.320
After she quit,

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:53.380
she rented a storefront on Limin Road

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:54.760
and opened a lingerie shop.

00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:56.690
It hasn't been open for a long time.

00:03:57.400 --> 00:03:59.240
We talked to the landlord.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.540
He said she planned to quit

00:04:01.560 --> 00:04:02.680
and move out of town for work.

00:04:02.680 --> 00:04:04.400
Did you find out about the man she was living with?

00:04:04.400 --> 00:04:04.960
Yes.

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:07.560
His name is Ma Jinguang.

00:04:07.560 --> 00:04:08.560
He's a miner.

00:04:14.880 --> 00:04:15.400
Go on.

00:04:15.720 --> 00:04:17.649
Five years ago at the KTV entrance,

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.519
over Kong Jiao,

00:04:18.519 --> 00:04:19.680
he got into a fight

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:21.120
and was administratively detained.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:22.440
That's when they met.

00:04:22.760 --> 00:04:23.360
Also,

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.640
a few hours before the incident,

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:27.920
he went to Kong Jiao's neighborhood.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:30.040
And the last call on Kong Jiao's phone

00:04:30.320 --> 00:04:31.600
was with Ma Jinguang.

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:32.480
What time?

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.360
10:00 PM.

00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:37.930
Captain Sun.

00:04:38.920 --> 00:04:39.680
We found out that

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:41.320
the night before Qiao Sisi was killed,

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:42.920
she went to a bar on Wu'an Road called

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.080
Yehai.

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:46.680
But it was peak hours back then.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.200
The waiter couldn't remember exactly what happened,

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:51.000
except for a very strange man beside her.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:52.280
This man was very careful.

00:04:52.280 --> 00:04:53.520
We checked the security cameras.

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:56.000
He was either facing away or looking down.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:57.080
We couldn't see his face at all.

00:04:57.080 --> 00:04:57.800
How did they leave?

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:58.920
They left in a taxi.

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:00.680
The license plate was 8350.

00:05:00.760 --> 00:05:02.200
I've sent it to the traffic department.

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:03.600
We should have news soon.

00:05:03.960 --> 00:05:04.320
Okay.

00:05:04.320 --> 00:05:05.650
Keep an eye on this lead.

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.200
I'll go bring Ma Jinguang in.

00:05:07.200 --> 00:05:08.460
Xiaohan, come with me.

00:05:09.480 --> 00:05:10.140
I'll go too.

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:20.320
Master, Brother Yan.

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:22.760
Xiaohan and I will ask the neighbors around.

00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:23.290
Let's go.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:55.840
Yan.

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:57.640
It's time to let it go.

00:05:57.840 --> 00:05:59.970
People can't live in the past forever.

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:03.560
The slag in the corridor

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:04.690
and the call records

00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:07.120
do make Ma Jinguang highly suspicious right now.

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:07.840
But right now,

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:09.160
we don't have clear evidence yet.

00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:10.360
Don't be impulsive later.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.690
We'll follow the rules.

00:06:12.840 --> 00:06:13.360
Okay.

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:24.650
Ma Jinguang.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:30.780
Are the police trying to break in?

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:31.920
We need to talk to you

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:32.800
about a few things.

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.240
I don't have time,

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:34.120
nor do I want to see you.

00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:35.450
Do you not want to see us,

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:36.880
or are you afraid to?

00:06:37.960 --> 00:06:38.690
Ma Jinguang.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.040
We're just asking questions now.

00:06:40.040 --> 00:06:41.920
Let's hope it doesn't become an interrogation.

00:06:41.920 --> 00:06:43.440
You should know the difference between the two.

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:44.159
Don't try to scare me.

00:06:44.159 --> 00:06:45.200
Arrest me if you want.

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:46.530
You're the cops anyway.

00:06:46.840 --> 00:06:49.100
Just like how you killed my dad back then.

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:50.880
Ah.

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:27.160
Come catch it.

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:27.810
Catch it.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:29.520
Hurry up.

00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:34.340
If you have no business here, just leave.

00:07:34.360 --> 00:07:35.360
Kong Jiao is dead.

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:40.880
Kong Jiao is dead.

00:07:47.960 --> 00:07:50.040
Jiaojiao called me a week ago,

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:52.560
and said she was going to Guangnan.

00:07:52.560 --> 00:07:53.960
Judging from her tone at the time,

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:55.690
she sounded quite determined.

00:07:57.280 --> 00:07:58.120
To do what?

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:58.850
I don't know.

00:07:58.880 --> 00:08:00.320
She just said she could make a lot of money.

00:08:00.320 --> 00:08:00.980
By herself,

00:08:01.200 --> 00:08:02.400
or with someone else?

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:03.600
I asked her,

00:08:03.600 --> 00:08:04.800
but she wouldn't say.

00:08:07.720 --> 00:08:09.180
Early morning on the 15th,

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:10.140
where were you?

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:14.840
Early morning on the 15th.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:19.740
I was probably at the mine the whole time.

00:08:19.880 --> 00:08:21.760
The elevator surveillance at Ziming Garden captured...

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:23.520
At 7:00 PM on the 14th,

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:25.160
you appeared at Kong Jiao's house.

00:08:25.160 --> 00:08:27.290
But there is no footage of you leaving.

00:08:27.520 --> 00:08:29.450
All the evidence points to you now.

00:08:29.480 --> 00:08:31.480
Do you think you can get away with it?

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:33.409
I didn't kill Jiaojiao.

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:37.400
The elevator was broken when I left.

00:08:37.400 --> 00:08:38.440
I took the stairs.

00:08:38.799 --> 00:08:39.799
That elevator

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:41.520
has been acting crazy lately.

00:08:41.520 --> 00:08:43.360
It runs around on its own all the time.

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:45.600
One minute it's running up from the basement,

00:08:45.600 --> 00:08:46.880
and the next, from the 30th floor,

00:08:46.880 --> 00:08:47.880
it scurries down.

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:49.690
What time did you leave?

00:08:50.600 --> 00:08:51.160
At 8:00.

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:52.280
I called her at 8:00,

00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:53.540
but she didn't answer.

00:08:58.760 --> 00:09:01.080
In the staircase where Kong Jiao was murdered,

00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:02.320
we found this slag.

00:09:03.800 --> 00:09:04.880
How do you explain this?

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.080
I'm a miner.

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:07.930
There's slag wherever I go.

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.920
Isn't that normal?

00:09:08.920 --> 00:09:10.720
Also, after I left Ziming Garden,

00:09:10.720 --> 00:09:11.680
I went back to the mine.

00:09:11.680 --> 00:09:15.140
The people working the night shift that day can testify for me.

00:09:15.240 --> 00:09:16.320
These injuries on Kong Jiao,

00:09:16.320 --> 00:09:17.920
you caused them, didn't you?

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:20.920
You have been physically abusing Kong Jiao all along.

00:09:23.560 --> 00:09:24.620
We had an argument.

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:27.840
It escalated,

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:29.330
and we got physical.

00:09:30.320 --> 00:09:31.520
But she hit me too.

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:32.920
She scratched me here,

00:09:32.920 --> 00:09:33.680
and bit me.

00:09:37.000 --> 00:09:38.400
What did you argue about?

00:09:43.280 --> 00:09:45.200
Didn't she work at a KTV before?

00:09:46.760 --> 00:09:49.560
After we got together, she promised not to go back.

00:09:50.640 --> 00:09:53.500
Coincidentally, the KTV she worked at closed down.

00:09:53.880 --> 00:09:55.210
So that was the end of it.

00:09:56.080 --> 00:09:58.540
But recently, her boss contacted her again.

00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:02.100
He said a client specifically asked for her.

00:10:03.880 --> 00:10:05.800
What guy could put up with that?

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:06.600
If it were you,

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:07.520
could you stand it?

00:10:07.520 --> 00:10:08.480
What was the KTV called?

00:10:08.480 --> 00:10:09.600
It's a bar now.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:10.840
It's called Yehai.

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:11.840
What's the manager's name?

00:10:11.840 --> 00:10:12.570
I don't know.

00:10:14.120 --> 00:10:15.380
His last name is Zhang.

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:12.440
Du.

00:11:12.520 --> 00:11:12.850
Huan.

00:11:17.040 --> 00:11:18.400
What are you doing tonight, Biao?

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:19.730
Mind your own business.

00:11:22.160 --> 00:11:22.890
Hello, Biao.

00:11:25.520 --> 00:11:26.320
Hey, Mr. Chen.

00:11:26.440 --> 00:11:27.240
Drink well.

00:11:28.520 --> 00:11:29.200
Hello, Biao.

00:11:29.200 --> 00:11:29.640
Hey.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:32.640
Biao.

00:11:32.640 --> 00:11:33.320
Stop talking.

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:34.360
Hurry, go in.

00:11:34.520 --> 00:11:35.080
Go in.

00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:17.400
Good evening, sir.

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:18.920
Do you have a reservation?

00:12:18.920 --> 00:12:20.720
If not, I can arrange one for you.

00:12:21.920 --> 00:12:23.920
Do I need a reservation to come here?

00:12:25.280 --> 00:12:27.000
I'm looking for your Manager Zhang.

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:27.680
Where is he?

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:29.320
Do you know him?

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:32.000
Sir.

00:12:32.000 --> 00:12:33.760
Are you kidding me?

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:36.160
Our boss is here to do business with your Manager Zhang.

00:12:36.160 --> 00:12:37.090
What do you want?

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:37.960
Where is he?

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:39.360
Is he playing hard to get?

00:12:39.680 --> 00:12:40.720
Do I know him?

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:42.920
Your Manager Zhang is a manager here.

00:12:42.920 --> 00:12:44.360
But he's just a punk to me.

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:45.040
You know?

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:48.200
Hurry up.

00:12:48.200 --> 00:12:48.960
Big business.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:50.440
Find him.

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:51.560
Sorry.

00:12:51.560 --> 00:12:52.600
Please wait a moment.

00:12:52.600 --> 00:12:53.660
I'll go inform him.

00:12:53.880 --> 00:12:54.680
Wait a minute.

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:02.560
Hey, Biao.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:05.120
Those guys downstairs are looking for you.

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:06.580
Which guys?

00:13:06.840 --> 00:13:07.200
Yes.

00:13:13.480 --> 00:13:14.610
Where are they from?

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:22.720
Let's be friends.

00:13:25.520 --> 00:13:25.920
Ouch.

00:13:25.920 --> 00:13:26.480
Sorry.

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:27.120
Come.

00:13:27.280 --> 00:13:27.840
Go up.

00:13:28.920 --> 00:13:30.050
Please go upstairs.

00:13:33.560 --> 00:13:34.320
Have a smoke.

00:13:34.400 --> 00:13:35.130
Have a smoke.

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:36.040
I don't smoke.

00:13:40.760 --> 00:13:42.200
You are Zhang Biao, right?

00:13:42.200 --> 00:13:42.760
Yeah.

00:13:44.840 --> 00:13:46.480
I need to ask you about something.

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:47.240
Please cooperate.

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:47.800
Oh.

00:13:48.520 --> 00:13:49.250
Captain Sun,

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:51.520
you're being too polite.

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:53.480
Police-civilian cooperation is expected.

00:13:53.480 --> 00:13:55.520
I will certainly tell you everything I know.

00:13:55.520 --> 00:13:56.080
Just ask.

00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:56.840
All right.

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.420
Help us identify someone.

00:13:58.600 --> 00:13:59.040
Oh.

00:14:00.520 --> 00:14:01.120
These two,

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:02.370
do you know them?

00:14:07.920 --> 00:14:09.920
I thought it was something serious.

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:10.800
Let me tell you.

00:14:10.800 --> 00:14:12.530
I have so many girls at my place.

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:14.160
How am I supposed to remember?

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:14.840
Right?

00:14:15.680 --> 00:14:16.340
Zhang Biao.

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:18.660
If we didn't have solid evidence,

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:20.360
we wouldn't have come to you.

00:14:21.320 --> 00:14:22.920
About the Huguang incident,

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:24.090
have you forgotten?

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:35.000
Look again.

00:14:36.800 --> 00:14:37.530
How about it?

00:14:38.200 --> 00:14:39.760
Can you recognize them now?

00:14:40.640 --> 00:14:41.320
Oh.

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:42.960
I recognize them.

00:14:43.000 --> 00:14:43.720
Let me see.

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:44.600
Ah.

00:14:44.760 --> 00:14:45.880
That Sisi,

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:47.120
and Jiaojiao.

00:14:47.840 --> 00:14:49.440
I recognize both of those girls.

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:51.120
They used to work at my place.

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:52.200
But

00:14:53.400 --> 00:14:55.260
they've been gone for a long time.

00:14:56.600 --> 00:14:57.840
About those two,

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:00.000
no matter what happened,

00:15:00.520 --> 00:15:01.650
tell me everything.

00:15:02.160 --> 00:15:02.840
Let's go.

00:15:03.560 --> 00:15:04.600
Thanks, Manager Zhang.

00:15:04.600 --> 00:15:06.000
Oh, don't mention it.

00:15:06.680 --> 00:15:07.480
Officers,

00:15:07.920 --> 00:15:09.480
why don't you hang out for a bit before leaving?

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:10.280
It's my treat.

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:12.280
I'll make sure everything is taken care of.

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:12.840
How about it?

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:13.360
Come on.

00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.560
Manager Zhang's arrangements,

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:15.960
we wouldn't dare accept.

00:15:16.120 --> 00:15:17.440
Keep an eye out recently.

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:18.320
If you hear anything,

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:19.280
let us know immediately.

00:15:19.280 --> 00:15:19.720
Okay, okay.

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:20.560
Definitely.

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:22.000
Oh, right.

00:15:22.800 --> 00:15:23.400
Um,

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:25.800
if you have any news about Jiaojiao and the others,

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:26.880
please let me know.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:29.320
After all, they've been with me for so many years.

00:15:29.320 --> 00:15:31.250
Those two girls are quite pitiful.

00:15:31.480 --> 00:15:32.540
In our line of work,

00:15:32.600 --> 00:15:33.360
life is hard.

00:15:34.520 --> 00:15:35.280
Hey, boss.

00:15:35.280 --> 00:15:36.560
The stuff you ordered is here.

00:15:36.560 --> 00:15:37.080
Oh.

00:15:37.080 --> 00:15:37.760
Take it upstairs first.

00:15:37.760 --> 00:15:38.360
Alright.

00:15:39.320 --> 00:15:40.400
I won't see you out then.

00:15:40.400 --> 00:15:40.800
Sure.

00:15:40.840 --> 00:15:41.400
Okay.

00:15:41.560 --> 00:15:42.560
See you next time.

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:46.330
Captain Sun.

00:15:47.560 --> 00:15:49.320
The taxi that took Qiao Sisi

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:50.760
has been called over.

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:51.400
Let's go.

00:15:51.400 --> 00:15:52.200
Let's ask him.

00:15:56.760 --> 00:15:57.280
Guys,

00:15:57.280 --> 00:15:58.410
where are you going?

00:15:59.320 --> 00:16:00.520
City criminal police.

00:16:00.520 --> 00:16:02.380
We need to ask you some questions.

00:16:02.840 --> 00:16:03.400
What?

00:16:03.760 --> 00:16:04.840
Wh-What happened?

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:06.420
Help us identify someone.

00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:07.200
This girl,

00:16:07.200 --> 00:16:08.200
have you seen her?

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:09.560
Her?

00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:10.600
I remember her.

00:16:10.800 --> 00:16:11.720
She took my cab.

00:16:12.520 --> 00:16:13.280
She was dressed

00:16:13.280 --> 00:16:14.600
pretty revealingly.

00:16:14.760 --> 00:16:16.960
You could tell she wasn't a decent girl.

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:18.770
Yeah.

00:16:18.880 --> 00:16:19.400
Oh, right.

00:16:19.400 --> 00:16:21.120
There was a man with her

00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:22.200
that night.

00:16:22.360 --> 00:16:23.080
A man

00:16:23.280 --> 00:16:24.010
was with her?

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:24.680
Yeah.

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:25.760
What did he look like?

00:16:25.760 --> 00:16:26.800
He was wearing a hat.

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:28.200
It was dark, so I didn't see clearly.

00:16:28.200 --> 00:16:28.800
Excuse me.

00:16:29.400 --> 00:16:30.460
Pull over up ahead.

00:16:31.000 --> 00:16:32.280
I need to buy some cigarettes.

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:33.140
Just stop here.

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:36.240
You're not there yet.

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:37.840
How about having one of mine?

00:16:39.040 --> 00:16:40.000
I can't smoke your cigarettes.

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:41.040
I smoke foreign brands.

00:16:41.040 --> 00:16:41.920
Thank you.

00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:43.960
Can you walk?

00:16:46.080 --> 00:16:47.040
So do you remember

00:16:47.040 --> 00:16:48.640
where that supermarket was?

00:16:48.760 --> 00:16:51.240
At that tobacco shop at the Wanfu intersection.

00:16:51.240 --> 00:16:51.840
Oh, right.

00:16:51.880 --> 00:16:52.920
That man

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:53.800
seemed to

00:16:53.800 --> 00:16:55.240
walk with a limp.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:58.520
That whole area is scheduled for demolition.

00:16:58.520 --> 00:17:01.050
There are no residential communities there.

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:04.760
Mr. Yan.